      <a href="/start-team" class="btn btn-secondary back-button">&larr; Back to Steps</a>
      <p class="step-label">Step 9 of 9</p>
      <h1>Prepare for Events</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Get ready for your first competition with a simple checklist and clear team roles.</p>
      <section class="content-section">
        <p>Before the event, make sure the robot runs, the pit is packed, and everyone knows what they are doing when they arrive.</p>
        <div class="content-subsection">
          <h3>Final checklist</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Pack robot, tools, chargers, batteries, and tape</li>
            <li>Print schedules, forms, and scouting sheets</li>
            <li>Assign match, pit, drive, and outreach responsibilities</li>
            <li>Review travel plans and event arrival times</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Action:</strong> Do a practice day before the event so the team can fix problems early.</p>
      </section>
      <div class="step-actions">
        <a href="/resources" class="btn btn-primary">View Resources &rarr;</a>
